{"tid":1659011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似死仲開心過生存","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T17:20:07.000Z","uid":46750,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbe25f16537a99b53098b359f1b7b44a98b9962","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:31:21.000Z","msg":"首先講明先，我暫時無自殺意圖。<br />\n<br />\n做人，要承受大量社會給予我地既價值觀。女既要靚有身材，男既要有錢。兩者都要有學歷。由細到大接受高壓既教育制度，長大仲要受階級較高嘅人壓着自己，難以向上爬。<br />\n<br />\n特別係香港，買唔到樓，普遍人一世做打工仔，日日阿諛奉承你上級你老細，但只係為咗個幾萬蚊人工，為左層樓捱生捱死。當你捱左幾廿年，最後你什麼都有了，卻沒有了青春，沒有了快樂。<br />\n<br />\n再加上香港依家咁既狀況，荒謬事情不斷發生，除左無力感，都係無力感，對香港無曬希望。睇完「小丑」套電影，男主角做一個正常人，符合社會價值觀嘅人係幾咁唔開心，但當做返小丑，反抗普遍世俗人定落嚟嘅社會價值觀，反而活得仲開心。我意思唔係話去殺人，但我地係唔係唔好再壓抑自己係呢個荒謬嘅社會入面，做一個解脫呢？"},{"pid":"2cc91693a0bafbc8ec13d61c569ab79f3e742916","tid":1659011,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"af0f724c1cfc6d82a48a446661b0fe40f27881ef","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"理性討論，唔洗叫我唔好自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a64ea6f2dc3ce34eeb0f17eeaba46a79acd9dd","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"有無人都認同呢種負面既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369760bf0f56d68c859883f99748d58035747fb0","tid":1659011,"uid":40407,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"某啲諗法其實係你太在意人地加上奴性又強先會咁<br />\n例如返工個例子<br />\n我對人好有禮貌<br />\n因為我覺得係做人嘅基本<br />\n但係我從未試過違背良心阿諛奉承老細<br />\n呢個世界又唔係得一份工<br />\n<br />\n不過我依家都唔開心，<br />\n因為擔心手足<br />\n一諗起佢地俾班無人性嘅恐怖分子虐待就好心痛"},{"pid":"f2f25ba3d7d4dcc4812c77e734f5afb82ef10b1b","tid":1659011,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"做人為自己而活最開心<br />\n講就咁講 難度好高"},{"pid":"adf11b65e8fb801263b108a8bd427f95f7ba4304","tid":1659011,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f25ba3d7d4dcc4812c77e734f5afb82ef10b1b","tid":1659011,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"做人為自己而活最開心<br />\n講就咁講 難度好高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce23340fd4e2e82f993252813af3e8223581353","tid":1659011,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a64ea6f2dc3ce34eeb0f17eeaba46a79acd9dd","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"有無人都認同呢種負面既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d49de892e8b7df994d0ae22f90ce8fc1414c056","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fce23340fd4e2e82f993252813af3e8223581353","tid":1659011,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a64ea6f2dc3ce34eeb0f17eeaba46a79acd9dd","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"有無人都認同呢種負面既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"無既，我份人都算樂觀，係睇完小丑得出黎既諗法，再回想返普遍人既人生，主要係香港，低下階層好大機會一世留係香港。香港呢個地方d人鍾意批評，生活壓力大，除非真係好有錢，你先算有d生活。唔係既話你一世做打工仔，日日驚遲到趕返工，又ot又剩，只係得幾萬蚊人工。自問活左咁耐，唔開心既事總比開心多，平時無話開心唔開心既時候，都會feel到個壓力好大，所以做唔出小丑咁殺人，咪做個解脫好似仲開心。"},{"pid":"03f4e670ea57057da691d03b415747ef690a32ca","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f25ba3d7d4dcc4812c77e734f5afb82ef10b1b","tid":1659011,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"做人為自己而活最開心<br />\n講就咁講 難度好高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"做到當然好，但又有幾多人做到。"},{"pid":"c700503034ec094489a5b867252e4a31ee9266a9","tid":1659011,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"係香港喳<br />\n移左民會好好多"},{"pid":"f529da29df6f3d384619f1ec1a551e693e622990","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c700503034ec094489a5b867252e4a31ee9266a9","tid":1659011,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"係香港喳<br />\n移左民會好好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"如果移唔到民既人，諗唔到係香港既生存意義"},{"pid":"cfae18c3498803f13d44d5c7fc10ae963cdbe239","tid":1659011,"uid":259088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"諗起一句話：物競天澤 適者生存"},{"pid":"120a62c2bcc44a0c929715c34032872a7a388bf3","tid":1659011,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係咪香港人尊專心太低<br />\n<br />\n好多時都要睇人地意願先去做，因為好驚會比人排斥同冷對<br />\n<br />\n變相自己冇理到自己嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n16年魚蛋革命，個個都屌太暴力，會影響街坊嚇親老人家小朋友，個時就算你支持勇武都唔會夠膽講出黎<br />\n<br />\n所以證明咗喺連登好易比人帶風向：個po咁多正評實好多人都buy樓主"},{"pid":"ce118b9d7087097eb96111e97f74012b4adf91d3","tid":1659011,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120a62c2bcc44a0c929715c34032872a7a388bf3","tid":1659011,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:55:59.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係咪香港人尊專心太低<br />\n<br />\n好多時都要睇人地意願先去做，因為好驚會比人排斥同冷對<br />\n<br />\n變相自己冇理到自己嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n16年魚蛋革命，個個都屌太暴力，會影響街坊嚇親老人家小朋友，個時就算你支持勇武都唔會夠膽講出黎<br />\n<br />\n所以證明咗喺連登好易比人帶風向：個po咁多正評實好多人都buy樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"自尊心"},{"pid":"c02dc3ba995fc8e15243030577699eafed658806","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:09:15.000Z","msg":"成日係到諗我呢d係咪太消極主義，但諗諗下點解消唔消極係由社會去定義。呢種擺脫痛苦較多既生活，係唔係先係積極既主義"},{"pid":"6429d103622e9f734c8ceb7af1dd270c6546576f","tid":1659011,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"唯有一有錢去晒旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb74800423565aac78776d283fa55d5e287046f","tid":1659011,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"屌你靚女喎 邊洗死"},{"pid":"941c9081aaec2d22642adb792b7dae84eb0f5735","tid":1659011,"uid":68717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"香港人太懦弱，包括我，好怕同人有衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da9f0c19b37edea199917861178e5b92d49f8cf","tid":1659011,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d49de892e8b7df994d0ae22f90ce8fc1414c056","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fce23340fd4e2e82f993252813af3e8223581353","tid":1659011,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a64ea6f2dc3ce34eeb0f17eeaba46a79acd9dd","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"有無人都認同呢種負面既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"無既，我份人都算樂觀，係睇完小丑得出黎既諗法，再回想返普遍人既人生，主要係香港，低下階層好大機會一世留係香港。香港呢個地方d人鍾意批評，生活壓力大，除非真係好有錢，你先算有d生活。唔係既話你一世做打工仔，日日驚遲到趕返工，又ot又剩，只係得幾萬蚊人工。自問活左咁耐，唔開心既事總比開心多，平時無話開心唔開心既時候，都會feel到個壓力好大，所以做唔出小丑咁殺人，咪做個解脫好似仲開心。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955873f3acf2694fdeefe1601de8e7d976f40d10","tid":1659011,"ui