9-10-17T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"可以訓訓下就走左咁真係好奢侈"},{"pid":"c3ca1a46f1494ad643bddf9c2d97081d98de7d7c","tid":1659011,"uid":269044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"在生既人羨慕死去既人<br />\n<br />\n如果普遍有呢個念頭，世界已經係末日緊"},{"pid":"60057238bc6103281cf086b7534f853f16393a92","tid":1659011,"uid":255536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30adc721f6c31578c79dfcb097f4c5a324a1662c","tid":1659011,"uid":78235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"就算未送中前既香港一樣無限OT, 成世為左一個格仔(唔好成日ff自己有一層樓， 我地只係得一個格仔， 連塊地都唔係你架)， 交租比起外國少令你覺得好似有好多cash咁但你老左食自己食仔女"},{"pid":"1f711c5b2799ce64d0ee585fd8b86fe4db33cc7b","tid":1659011,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cbe25f16537a99b53098b359f1b7b44a98b9962","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:31:21.000Z","msg":"首先講明先，我暫時無自殺意圖。<br />\n<br />\n做人，要承受大量社會給予我地既價值觀。女既要靚有身材，男既要有錢。兩者都要有學歷。由細到大接受高壓既教育制度，長大仲要受階級較高嘅人壓着自己，難以向上爬。<br />\n<br />\n特別係香港，買唔到樓，普遍人一世做打工仔，日日阿諛奉承你上級你老細，但只係為咗個幾萬蚊人工，為左層樓捱生捱死。當你捱左幾廿年，最後你什麼都有了，卻沒有了青春，沒有了快樂。<br />\n<br />\n再加上香港依家咁既狀況，荒謬事情不斷發生，除左無力感，都係無力感，對香港無曬希望。睇完「小丑」套電影，男主角做一個正常人，符合社會價值觀嘅人係幾咁唔開心，但當做返小丑，反抗普遍世俗人定落嚟嘅社會價值觀，反而活得仲開心。我意思唔係話去殺人，但我地係唔係唔好再壓抑自己係呢個荒謬嘅社會入面，做一個解脫呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"放縱固然開心 <br />\n但因為有節制有法律<br />\n先令你嘅開心唔會帶俾人不幸<br />\n<br />\nbtw 小丑 我覺得拍得無想像中咁好睇<br />\n建議你睇吓美劇Mr. Robot"},{"pid":"323031decfecc194221d28d02c9b038995460a9c","tid":1659011,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b4cfcbee7d5550d06cb9563105ce6e5c75bba1","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eb74800423565aac78776d283fa55d5e287046f","tid":1659011,"uid":243175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"屌你靚女喎 邊洗死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"靚女都會唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"想問你會唔會痾屎？<br />\n係咪因為便秘所以唔開心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f97175274694bf754abd56714fd8a1a37190e6e","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa94b11dde78c03c10e49a6f62b15f1ea4e4efb","tid":1659011,"uid":153570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5674f69b4646e1f849945cdb0e40f5bd3486cc9a","tid":1659011,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想快啲死 不過唔會自殺 成日都想有啲意外搞到我死咗仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"可以訓訓下就走左咁真係好奢侈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"呢件事可以話係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d61ef06b67f20330f3b941d7a96a7acf0b9e8f8","tid":1659011,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"快樂點解唔可以好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa9a92cfa0fd35ec96024c57ee19ec1fb632339","tid":1659011,"uid":46750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d61ef06b67f20330f3b941d7a96a7acf0b9e8f8","tid":1659011,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"快樂點解唔可以好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"how"},{"pid":"1e27157454f7b0ece41363cc57c685f3f60d9b30","tid":1659011,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"你呢啲人就係真